title: Ohio, Foxes & The Kentucky Derby
description: Fellas discuss the Ohio Senate race and news about another killer fox before welcoming Rep. Andy Barr from Kentucky for an interview about the Derby and more. Utah Treasurer Marlo Oaks also joins the progrum.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Comfortably Smug, Josh Holmes, Michael Duncan, John Ashbrook, Andy Barr, Marlo Oaks)
